channel.title: Adding models (PI)
channel.description: I am using the Exion source, and followed this tutorial: [url=http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-client/tutorials/235346-pi-adding-dragon-claws-client-sided-pi.html]http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-client/tutorials/235346-pi-adding-dragon-claws-client-sided-pi.html[/url] It worked up until when i tried to run my client and it gave me the "Sorry, an error has occured while loading..." cmd prompt states that i got a " load error 95" -which i suspect is preloading the models. All help is appreciated. :)
